actor "BC" as bc #ffffff
participant "loan" as la
participant "asset" as ass
participant "loan(loancore)" as lc
participant "core" as core

== 改造前 ==
bc->la:贷款试算
la->lc:贷款试算
lc-->>la:试算结果
la-->>bc:试算结果

bc->la:申请还款\nbcrefno
la->core:借客户账
core-->>la:记账结果
la->lc:贷贷款户
lc-->>la:记账结果
la-->>bc:还款结果

== 改造后 ==
bc->la:贷款试算
la->lc:贷款试算
lc-->>la:试算结果
la-->>bc:试算结果

bc->la:申请还款\nbcrefno
la->ass:借客户账
ass->core:借客户账
core-->>ass:记账结果
ass-->>la:记账结果
la->lc:贷贷款户
lc-->>la:记账结果
la-->>bc:还款结果

@endUml